text: Colobothea rincona is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Giesbert in 1979. It is known from Costa Rica.BioLib.cz - Colobothea rincona. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1979
title: Colobothea rincona
